                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                    oc:textContent "Draft a complete offer letter for a new hire." ],
                [ a oc:BlockQuote ;
                    oc:blockType "blockquote" ;
                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                    oc:quoteContent "If you see unfamiliar placeholders or need to check which tools are connected, see [CONNECTORS.md](../../CONNECTORS.md)." ] ;
            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                            oc:codeContent """## Offer Letter Draft: [Role] — [Level]

### Compensation Package
| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Base Salary** | $[X]/year |
| **Equity** | [X shares/units], [vesting schedule] |
| **Signing Bonus** | $[X] (if applicable) |
| **Target Bonus** | [X]% of base (if applicable) |
| **Total First-Year Comp** | $[X] |

### Terms
- **Start Date**: [Date]
- **Reports To**: [Manager]
- **Location**: [Office / Remote / Hybrid]
- **Employment Type**: [Full-time, Exempt]

### Benefits Summary
[Key benefits highlights relevant to the candidate]

### Offer Letter Text

Dear [Candidate Name],

We are pleased to offer you the position of [Title] at [Company]...

[Complete offer letter text]

### Notes for Hiring Manager
- [Negotiation guidance if needed]
- [Comp band context]
- [Any flags or considerations]
""" ;
                            oc:codeLanguage "markdown" ;
